metadata.name: BLEU DE XATYNE
metadata.description:
clasification of senunuku creatures and other "se" creatures. in xatinian language, "se" is the word for "sky". these creatures live in the sky. they were spotted by mexican neuroscientist and Xatin culture researcher Dr. Vicente Ventura

among these creatures there are "yksekuku", "ykykomom", "ykomtzyltzyl", "tolykse", among others

it could be interesting to note that Dr. Vicente Ventura presented this clasification in a similar composition from the painting "blue de ciel" from the russian painter Wassily Kandinsky
